parameters:
Hey... Did you see Bell-senpai from the Selection Exam!?
That person is just too amazing...! The flowing long hair
and the dignified gaze... Sigh, I wish I could be stared at
too...

Oh... I was completely captivated by that person. I even
accidentally joined their fan club myself...

...Maybe I should join too. They say she's the next Lunaroa,
you know...

\SE[5] (I wonder if Lunaroa was also seen like this during
her student days? \SE[24] It's both proud and...
complicated...)

Hey... Did you see Bell-senpai from the Selection Exam!?
That person is just too amazing...! The flowing long hair
and the dignified gaze... Sigh, I wish I could be stared at
too...

Oh... I was completely captivated by that person. I even
accidentally joined their fan club myself...

...Maybe I should join too. They say she's the reincarnation
of Lunaroa, you know...

\SE[5] (I wonder if Lunaroa was also seen like this during
her student days? \SE[24] It's both proud and...
complicated...)

Afternoon classes are so boring... Should I just skip... But
my credits are at risk...

Lately, I've been receiving more books from Yuriseen. Right
now, the most popular one is the book about Kenkoku. The two
great heroes, Soare and Ashamusu...  Note: The names
Yuriseen, Kenkoku, Soare, and Ashamusu are left untranslated
as they appear to be specific terms or names within the
context.

The friendship between these two is highly praised as
precious. However... there is constant controversy over the
order of multiplication and the surrounding community is
constantly in an uproar.

\SE[3] (Well, it's impossible to think of anything other
than the classic Soare x Ale pairing.)

Seriously, even though it's confirmed that Ale x Soare is
the way to go... those heretics who support Soare x Ale
are...

This is the 'Magic Academy'! I also want to enroll here and
become a great 'magician' someday! Are you also aspiring to
become a 'magician'?

Wow...!! Then maybe we could be classmates! It would be
great if we could be in the same class!
Is that so...! Then, what did you come here for...?

The door won't open... It seems like a magic spell has been
cast to prevent outsiders from entering.
